## Surveyed paths

- proposals/PROP-0005-quote-detail-census-editable.md — design contract.
- docs/spec/common/CommonData.data — DSL canonical shapes:
  - `AggregateCensus { headcount: int, planBreakdown: list<PlanHeadcount{planNo, headcount}> }`
  - `CensusFileFormat { fileType: CensusFileType, sheetName?, schemaJson, dialectJson? }`
  - `enum CensusFileType { CSV, XLSX }`
- docs/spec/quotation/QuotationDomain.domain — `updateAggregateCensus(census)` and `updateCensusFileFormat(format)`; both `precondition isDraft`. No `hasCensusFileFormat` precondition on updateAggregateCensus, so headcount edits are allowed before file format is set (good — UI doesn't need to gate that).
- schemas/tabs/quote/census.json — current key-value-grid surface (will be rewritten).
