- src/components/ui/table.tsx — primitive (`Table`, `TableHeader`, `TableRow`, `TableCell`, etc.).
- src/components/widgets/forms/formContainer/ — scalar-only FormContainer. CensusFileFormat fields are all scalar (fileType select, sheetName text, schemaJson + dialectJson as textareas) so the file-format edit form fits cleanly.
